data.description: Welcome to your new home at 506 Chestnut Walk in the sought-after community of Bridgemill. This home has been renovated with new and refinished hardwood flooring throughout main floor, new carpet upstairs and in the basement, new appliances and quartz countertops in kitchen, beautiful new statement lighting fixtures on main level and fresh paint throughout the entire home.  My clients have done all of the work, so you don't have to. Just pack your boxes and move right in. Rest easy knowing the water heater and furnaces are all new. Step outside to a golfer's dream view of TEE 5. The yard is spacious with room for pets, family and outdoor entertaining. In-Law Suite: Basement has a bedroom, bathroom, living space, kitchenette and dining space perfect for an in-law suite. Workshop: There is a workshop located in the basement along with additional storage room and additional storage space in garage for bike, strollers, wagons, etc. Convenient Location: Located in a sought-after area of Canton, this home offers easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and major commuting routes, not to mention all of the community amenities of golf, tennis and pool. Don't miss this opportunity to make 506 Chestnut Walk your new address. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of modern updates and timeless charm in coveted Bridgemill.
